OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLorry driver shortage:     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FTemporary visa scheme to   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fend on Christmas Eve       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A temporary visa scheme to make it     
OL,6, easier for foreign lorry drivers to    
OL,7, work in the UK is to run for three     
OL,8, months, ending on Christmas eve.       
OL,10,FIt is understood that about 5,000      
OL,11,Ftemporary visas could be issued, with  
OL,12,Fmore details expected on Sunday.       
OL,14,FA shortage of drivers has disrupted    
OL,15,Ffuel deliveries, with some petrol      
OL,16,Fstations closing, and queues forming.  
OL,18,FThe government said there was no fuel  
OL,19,Fshortage at refineries, and urged      
OL,20,Fpeople not to panic buy.               
